&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bank ICU Nurse &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Locations: Salford Royal Hospital, North Manchester General Hospital, The Royal Oldham Hospital &amp; Fairfield General Hospital&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pay Rates: Band 7.9 - &lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Day £23.4 / Night &amp; Sat £30.42 / Sun &amp; BH £37.44&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Do you have experience in providing exceptional support as an Intensive Care Nurse?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you looking to return to work in a hospital setting?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you looking to keep your General skills up while you are specialising in an ICU role?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Do you want to Support your Local hospital by working Bank shifts?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;If you have answered yes to the above, please contact us as soon as possible. We are looking for registered nurses to work in ICU for 3 months. Various shift patterns to suit your lifestyle.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As one of the largest employers, The Northern Care Alliance (Salford Royal trust and The Pennine Acute hospitals) is the thriving heart of the local community with the busiest Emergency Departments in the North West.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Northern Care Alliance provides high quality care to patients within Salford and the surroundings , Bury, Rochdale Oldham .Do you want to work for the biggest and busiest organization in the North West?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a NHS Professionals Flexible Bank Worker you will support the department in all aspects of care that the Trust expect from our workers, you will have the knowledge and passion to support colleagues and patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you want to be a part of a fantastic team and help support the Trust with their vision for providing the best in the country, then we want to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you answered ‘Yes’ to the above, we’d love to hear from you!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Skills/Responsibilities &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To apply for these posts, you will:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Have a minimum of 6 months paid experience as a Registered Nurse in a hospital environment within the last 2 years&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Comply with NMC Professional Registration and keep up to date with current nursing practices&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Undertake nursing assessment and evaluation to enable development of appropriate plans of care based on the needs of the individual&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be proficient in the delivery of care to patients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure safe administration of drugs in accordance with NMC and CHS policies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure accurate records are kept in accordance with CHS policy and NMC guidelines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Carry out nursing procedures and techniques in accordance with agreed policies and standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Undertake regular mandatory training&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In return for your hard work and caring skills, we can offer you some fantastic benefits:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Competitive Pay Rates - &lt;/strong&gt;work this week, get paid next week!&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;First choice of shifts at your Trust&lt;/strong&gt; – Access to shifts before they are available to agency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Flexible working to suit your lifestyle &lt;/strong&gt;– Take control of when you want to work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Build holiday allowance for every shift you work &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Book and manage your shifts on the go&lt;/strong&gt; – Access shifts anywhere, anytime online or through your smartphone&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Support when you need it – 24/7 365 days – &lt;/strong&gt;Call us anytime on 03332 407 552&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stakeholder pension scheme&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
